ween English and Indonesian non-verbal predicates and the contrast of the English copula be and the Indonesian copulas ada and adalah. The lingusitic description is done in a generative DM-based approach. Thus, this volume does not only provide new insights in the field language acquisiton, but also in the generative description of Indonesian in general and non-verbal predicates in particular.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aEnglish languagexGrammarxStudy and teaching. 0aEnglish languagexStudy and teachingxIndonesian speakers. 0aEnglish languagexVerb phrase. 0aIndonesian languagexVerb phrase. 0aSecond language acquisition. 4aEnglisch. 4aIndonesisch. 4aKopula. 4aNichtverbale Prädikate. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aCopula.  aGrammar Competition.  aIndonesian.  aNon-Verbal Predicates.  aSecond Language Acquisition.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1z978311117578208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter Mouton eBook Package 2023z978311120579308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2023 Englishz978311131916208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2023z9783111318240oZDB-23-DSP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertMouton eBook Package 2022z97831107912970 cEPUBz97831107663700 cprintz978311076625740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311076633240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110766332423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110766332/original  a978-3